    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "```\nIn [1]: s = Series(np.random.randn(5))\n\nIn [2]: s[1] = np.nan\n\nIn [3]: s[2] = np.inf\n\nIn [4]: s[3] = -np.inf\n\nIn [5]: s\nOut[5]: \n0    0.760816\n1         NaN\n2         inf\n3        -inf\n4    0.441029\ndtype: float64\n\nIn [6]: s.dropna()\nOut[6]: \n0    0.760816\n2         inf\n3        -inf\n4    0.441029\ndtype: float64\n```\n\nYou can already do this\n\n```\nIn [12]: with pd.option_context('use_inf_as_null',True):\n   ....:     print(s.dropna())\n   ....:     \n0    0.760816\n4    0.441029\ndtype: float64\n```\n"
  },
